Polarization spectra published in "Polarized kilonovae from black hole-neutron star mergers", Bulla et al. (2021)

Feel free to use these models and cite the relevant publications listed in citations.bib

1) FILENAME

BHNS-X_Y.txt
X: model (Dyn/DynWind)
Y: viewing angle (see Fig. 3 and Fig. 4 of Bulla et al. 2021)

2) FILE FORMAT

One file each model each viewing angle

##########################################################################

#################### iobs = 0 ############################################
                 itime=0   itime=0   itime=1   itime=1   itime=2   itime=2
                 (1.5 d)   (1.5 d)   (2.5 d)   (2.5 d)   (3.5 d)   (3.5 d)
